        <h2><a href="/series/best-2010">The Best of 2010 Series</a></h2>      </span>
  </div>
      <div class="views-field-body">
                <div class="field-content">
        A recap of some of 2010's biggest events including: the BP oil spill, the earthquake in Haiti, and Health Care Reform.
And from Ira Glass chatting about the value of public radio, to Pulitzer Prize winning journalist Isabel Wilkerson's epic story on America's great migration, and George Romero mapping out the creative process of a zombie film -- enjoy this year's staff favorites as well.      </div>
